[Groovy] Class ListDiff

java.lang.Object
  edu.holycross.shot.listutils.ListDiff

class ListDiff

A class for working with a pair of ordered lists to compare. Implementation of the Longest Common Sequence algorithm is based on the discussion at http://www.cs.princeton.edu/introcs/96optimization/LCS.java.html
